---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Riya Hariyaplar | Interests</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --text: #122033;
        --muted: #4f6480;
        --accent: #2f6fed;
        --green: #6c9f5f;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #eef8f0 100%);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .container {
        width: min(1100px, 92%);
        margin: auto;
      }

      nav {
        background: white;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5eaf3;
      }

      .nav-inner {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        margin-left: 1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .active {
        color: var(--green);
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 3.5rem;
      }

      .subtitle {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: auto;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      section {
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }

      .card {
        background: white;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid #e5eaf3;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .two {
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      }

      .bottom {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav>
      <div class="container nav-inner">
        <div><strong>Riya Hariyaplar</strong></div>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">About</a>
          <a href="/resume">Resume</a>
          <a href="/skills">Skills</a>
          <a href="/interests" class="active">Interests</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
      <h1>Interests</h1>

      <p class="subtitle">
        🌿 How many hidden leaves did you find on this site?
      </p>

      <!-- MAIN SECTION -->
      <section class="grid two">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Camping & National Parks</h3>
          <p>
            I love being outdoors and exploring nature. I have been to 14 national parks and love camping, road trips, and scenic environments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Photography</h3>
          <p>
            Photography is one of my favorite creative outlets. I love capturing moments, textures, and colors.
          </p>
          <a href="/photos">View gallery</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- SUSTAINABILITY -->
      <section>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Sustainability & Climate Advocacy</h3>
          <p>
            I am passionate about sustainability and climate policy. I have written [insert number] letters to the editor on climate-related topics and have been involved in advocacy efforts around carbon policy.
          </p>

          <p>
            I worked with the team around Ro Khanna, a U.S. Representative, to better understand climate legislation and policy impact.
          </p>

          <p>
            <a href="https://citizensclimatelobby.org/blog/policy/hr763-the-bipartisan-climate-change-solution/" target="_blank">
              Read about the Carbon Dividend bill
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FUN SECTION -->
      <section class="grid bottom">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Current Book</h3>
          <p>The Secret Lives of Color</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Podcast Interest</h3>
          <p>Child developmental psychology</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Favorite Dessert</h3>
          <p>
            Banana bread is such a fun dessert to bake and experiment with because it can never go poorly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      2026 Riya Hariyaplar
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
